<li>Nuspec enhancements - supported versions of Windows, etc</li>
<li>Packaging enhancements - like package version, architecture</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/chocolatey/chocolatey/issues/7">Virtual packages</a></li>
<li>WSA Support</li>
<li>Windows Nano Support - likely late 2016/early 2017 (switching to .NET Standard/Core)</li>
</ul>
